	('Battlefield 4', ' is a first-person shooter video game developed by video game developer EA DICE and published by Electronic Arts. It is a sequel to 2011 Battlefield 3 and was released in October 2013 for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 3, and Xbox 360; then later in November for PlayStation 4 and Xbox One.', 'Shooter', 30),
